annotationA: CG1492, isoform A; Gamma-glutamyltransferase activity. It is involved in the biological process described with: glutathione metabolic process
annotationB: Gamma-glutamylcyclotransferase; Catalyzes the cleavage of glutathione into 5-oxo-L- proline and a Cys-Gly dipeptide. Acts specifically on glutathione, but not on other gamma-glutamyl peptides
